{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"331254-menina-telefone","title":"Menina Telefone","description":"Ms Phone is quite a character! Can you imagine having five phones, for communicating with different people?","language":"Portuguese","langCode":"pt","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Isabel Ferreira","Translators withoutBorders"],"illustrators":["Marion  Drew"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/331254-menina-telefone"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/418455/size3/c7f1693f5da71731ca8cd6c959dcf329.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/418455/size6/c7f1693f5da71731ca8cd6c959dcf329.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415391/size6/4fec3510478c06562dfbca4c7deaaa04.jpg","text":"Chamam-lhe a Menina Telefone. Olhem para ela!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415393/size6/aa5c4a109dec9452b7cb7d2640909eef.jpg","text":"Tem cinco telemóveis. Quando acorda, coloca os telemóveis por ordem sobre a mesa.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415394/size6/b8bd6e821970b3f78c0e8402835704c2.jpg","text":"O amarelo é para comunicar com a família.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415395/size6/342e3bad30e3bebd7b92fc729d956cb1.jpg","text":"O branco para comunicar com os colegas de trabalho.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415396/size6/add4ce17ad772d77012081aa2392c23c.jpg","text":"O vermelho é para comunicar com pessoas que lhe devem alguma coisa.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415398/size6/8d7e688c2738ab39d2e3bf1f7063ba75.jpg","text":"O cor-de-rosa é para comunicar com os seus melhores amigos.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415399/size6/933146190c0a2bbf7a8b6c90b4daaa29.jpg","text":"O roxo é para comunicar com as pessoas que precisam da sua ajuda.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415400/size6/736e57187eb30c18da2edd31074ac168.jpg","text":"A Menina Telefone quer que as pessoas sejam felizes. Não gosta de brigas.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415401/size6/de0b998d9cd6e95844eb211c0e2dbc17.jpg","text":"Deixa que as crianças vejam televisão na sua loja.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415404/size6/d93c7546abac037780c154399866861b.jpg","text":"Visita as casas dos doentes e dos idosos.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415406/size6/54e0f0ba678913a2af1354ba5d176f76.jpg","text":"Quando passa, escutam-se os gritos de \"Menina Telefone! Menina Telefone!\"","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415409/size6/e31af71c5252fd79ff2a49b505e56f25.jpg","text":"Nessas alturas, ela sente-se feliz e diz: \"Sou a Menina Telefone – vejam os meus telefones!\" Assim é a Menina Telefone com os seus cinco telemóveis.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":138}}